</h2><p><core-commerce id="57cf59a9edcc4902bd63ba9e64e29526" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> 65 英寸<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWSEJMVjRZP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYfBw4MrOnJYYE8BRcfLcnhnQMT4qB9z-vuhlsjDMAzi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09VHBLV4Y" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09VHBLV4Y?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星 S95B</a>售价为 1,598 美元，创下历史最低价。通常情况下，这套高评价的套装近几个月要额外花费 100 至 200 美元。 S95B 的 QD-OLED 面板将 OLED 技术与量子点层相结合，使其能够提供高对比度和宽视角，而不会在亮度和色彩饱和度方面牺牲典型 OLED 电视的性能。这意味着即使在更明亮的房间里它也应该提供丰富的图像。它还可以播放高达 4K 120Hz 的内容，这对于 PS5 或 Xbox Series X 来说很方便，但与所有三星电视一样，它不支持杜比视界 HDR。</p><h2> Roku 流媒体棒 4K </h2><p><core-commerce id="a951b7335461496a8c2065343c3321d3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARJVYosyubwwiQK-9l5WJrXDrYWySaExRtYSwdG8zZ_h&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoku-Streaming-Device-Vision-Controls%2Fdp%2FB09BKCDXZC%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Roku 的 Streaming Stick 4K</a>目前已降至 34 美元，比平常价格低 16 美元。它是我们目前最喜欢的<a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-streaming-devices-media-players-123021395.html">流媒体设备</a>，因为它在价格实惠的套餐中包含了大量功能。它通过杜比视界传输 4K、HDR 内容，并支持 AirPlay 2 和使用耳机进行私人聆听。</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel 7a </h2><p><core-commerce id="df64cb2397694fb6b5e5537076438d29" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJaOVhOQlJCP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZdaBFLB-Ahof3YN2aCDcywk9K2CpFe-s_n5pm9DV10p&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BZ9XNBRB" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BZ9XNBRB?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Pixel 7a</a>目前售价 449 美元，比平时便宜 50 美元，创下历史新低。由于其快速的 Tensor G2 芯片、流畅的 90Hz 显示屏以及对无线充电的支持，这是您现在可以获得<a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-engadget-guide-to-the-best-midrange-smartphones-120050366.html">的最好的中端手机</a>。 7a 还配备坚固的摄像头和 IP67 防水设计。</p><h2> Nest <strong>WiFi Pro - 3 件装</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="fffd5a9dd59d4ab895480eeb53159906" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWWNiyOPcwh0W_aJm-KPH0PCSQju7IqbwCyB5i2teIG5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Nest-WiFi-Pro-Reliable%2Fdp%2FB0BCQS55N6" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Nest WiFi Pro 三件套</a>为您提供与这对产品相同的技术，但范围更广。使用三个路由器，您可以在 6,600 平方英尺的范围内访问 WiFi。三件套产品享受 25% 的折扣，售价为 300 美元，因此每台 Nest WiFi Pro 只需 100 美元——考虑到它们通常的零售价为每台 200 美元，这真是太划算了。至于颜色，全部选择雪色，或者混合使用雪色、雾色和亚麻色。</p><h2>雷蛇猎魂迷你版</h2><p><core-commerce id="39fd7b5804234803adc09589a166e639" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>紧凑型<a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd2S9ZVEGupLeKU_fxLjP70G3RJDlpZC8MvCrnx69kIN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08BFF4C7J%2F&amp;uuid=x3oFAYDJGNZTkzRN68940">Razer Huntsman Mini</a>现已降至 68 美元，比平时便宜 43%。这两笔交易都不是历史最低价，但过去几个月这两款机型的零售价通常在 80 至 100 美元之间。 Huntsman Mini 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-60-percent-keyboards-160038272.html">60% 最佳键盘</a>指南中的首选，因为它的按键舒适且对游戏反应始终如一。整个东西感觉做工精良，每个按键都有优质的 PBT 键帽和 RGB 灯光。每个键也可以通过宏进行编程。不过，对于那些喜欢弹性和触感更好的人来说，这里的开关并不理想，而且超紧凑的设计并不适合所有人。</p><h2>罗技 Litra Glow </h2><p><core-commerce id="3e1c4888c81c412693a0ba306c29ea73" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>直播主播或任何想要在镜头上看起来更好的人都应该在打折时购买<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOTdRWkdSQ1E_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXBtLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyZTBiODVjNC1kNTZiLTQ3NzUtOTI0Yi02YjJjZTUzMGE3MTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQ9m3H9rm8IzjhMnPrJaxya75cAH-QFVD5g_MUjc6QC0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB097QZGRCQ" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B097QZGRCQ?" class="rapid-with-clickid">罗技的 Litra Glow LED 灯</a>。我们在指南中推荐它，因为 USB 供电的设备可发出漫射、柔和的光芒，没有刺眼的阴影，并配有可扩展的显示器支架。</p><h2>雷蛇灵刃 15 </h2><p><core-commerce id="d3a9d9c682b24277991fdd62df07d2bc" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliat